name: Time Stood Still
description: An abstract digital collage using AI generated images as source material for the collage paired with my own custom digital graphics! This is the 4th machine collab in the series! Time Stood Still reflects on blissful moments in nature that leave you awestruck. Moments in time that were so beautiful you couldn't help but just stand there amazed. We humans romanticize much of this life, with our rose tinted glasses & our love for beauty, among other things.. but some moments I feel romanticize us. I hoped to capture this feeling here with this machine collaboration / digital collage. I myself can't seem to take off the rose tinted glasses.. & why would I want to? Some moments we just want to live in forever.
